official_title: Assessing the Impact of a Community Health Worker on Hispanic Women's Reported Measures of Processes of Care in the Screening Mammography Setting
inclusion_criteria:
* Women
* Identifying as Hispanic ethnicity
* Age 40-64
* Tennessee resident
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 40 Years
Must have maximum age of 64 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Personal history of breast cancer
* Current breast symptoms (palpable mass)
